Develop Charity Volunteer Management system: Create src/pages/charity/volunteer with volunteer portal featuring registration with skills/availability, opportunity browsing with filtering, application management, schedule calendar with shift assignments, hour tracking, and certificate generation. Build admin interface (src/pages/admin/charity/VolunteerManager.tsx) for opportunity posting, application review, volunteer assignment, hour verification, communication tools (email/SMS), and volunteer analytics (engagement, impact, retention). Implement features: volunteer profiles with skills/interests, automated matching to opportunities, reminder notifications, volunteer appreciation (badges, recognition), and volunteer training resources. Store in GitHub DB: volunteers, volunteer_opportunities, volunteer_applications, volunteer_hours, volunteer_assignments, volunteer_certificates with proper workflow management.
